parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent brake failure can cause loss of braking power, leading to accidents or near-misses, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake light comes on
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sinks to the floor
loud grinding or metallic noises
vibration in the brake pedal
and loss of braking power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear suspension can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, and can also lead to rust and corrosion of the vehicle's frame, compromising its structural integrity.
symptoms: The vehicle sways from left to right
the rear tires bounce or vibrate
the steering wheel vibrates
the vehicle is difficult to control
and there is a loud popping or clanking sound.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents, and can also lead to vibrations in the steering wheel and difficulty controlling the vehicle.
symptoms: The brake light comes on
the vehicle shakes or vibrates when braking
the steering wheel vibrates
the vehicle is difficult to stop
and there is a loud grinding or springing noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust and corrosion of the vehicle's frame can compromise its structural integrity, leading to accidents, and can also lead to the failure of the rear suspension and other components.
symptoms: The vehicle's frame is rusted or corroded
the rear suspension is damaged
and there is a loud popping or clanking sound.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch system can cause the vehicle to lose power and stall, leading to accidents, and can also lead to difficulty shifting gears.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
and there is a loud grinding or springing noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended airbag deployment can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities. It can also lead to financial losses, emotional distress, and loss of vehicle usage.
symptoms: Sudden deployment of airbags without any impact or crash
airbag light flashing on the dashboard
airbag warning light staying on
and failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag sensor failure can lead to unintended airbag deployment, failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, or incorrect airbag warnings, which can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Airbag light flashing on the dashboard
airbag warning light staying on
incorrect airbag warnings
and failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake failure can cause accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Grinding or loose brakes
sudden loss of brake function
and emergency light turning on.
